      "content": "AI & Machine Learning | Google Cloud Blog AI & Machine Learning Find news, updates, and best practices for AI and machine learning solutions on Google Cloud. AI & Machine Learning Introducing Gemini 3.1 Pro on Google Cloud Today, we’re announcing Gemini 3.1 Pro on Google Cloud for developers and business teams. Get started on Gemini CLI, Gemini Enterprise, and Vertex AI. By Michael Gerstenhaber • 2-minute read Read article AI & Machine Learning Pro-level image generation gets faster and more accessible with Nano Banana 2 By Michael Gerstenhaber • 3-minute read AI & Machine Learning What Google Cloud announced in AI this month By Andrea Sanin • 9-minute read News in short A quick take on updates, announcements, resources, events, and learning opportunities from Google Cloud in one handy location. Updated weekly. Read now Infrastructure How WPP accelerates humanoid robot training 10x with G4 VMs By Perry Nightingale • 5-minute read Media & Entertainment Building the agentic future: A spotlight on Google Cloud’s media & entertainment partner ecosystem By Anshul Kapoor • 5-minute read AI & Machine Learning Claude Opus 4.7 on Vertex AI By Michael Gerstenhaber • 3-minute read Customers Cool stuff Google Cloud customers built, April edition: BMW big on SLMs, MLB’s Scout Insights AI, personalized resort experiences By Google Cloud Content & Editorial • 8-minute read AI & Machine Learning Multi-region endpoints are available for Claude on Vertex AI By Chase Lyall • 6-minute read AI & Machine Learning Guide to prompting Gemini 3.1 Flash TTS (text-to-speech) By Wendi Ding • 6-minute read AI & Machine Learning How to find the sweet spot between cost and performance By Federico Vibrati • 10-minute read Security & Identity Raising the security baseline: Essential AI and cloud security now on by default By Griselda Cuevas • 3-minute read AI & Machine Learning How SAP Concur automates expense reporting with agentic AI By Matt Wilkerson • 6-minute read Media & Ente